      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm a high school debate coach and i have a group of students prepping for a tournament next week. one of the resolutions is about immigration policy. can you help me out by steelmanning the arguments for increased border security and stricter immigration enforcement? i want my students to have the strongest possible version of that position so they can actually prepare for it, rather than just fighting against weak or surface-level points.",
